    "en": {
      "title": "Dhammika's chair three to battle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to sources, a three-cornered fight has been created for the position of National List Member of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, which has been left vacant by the resignation of prominent businessman Dhammika Perera.",
        "It has been learned that the ruling secretary of the party Renuka Perera, Southern Province Governor Willy Gamage Gamage and S. Amarasinghe are trying to get the seat.",
        "It is said that they have submitted requests to the founder and national organizer of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Mr. Basil Rajapaksa through various persons."
      ],
